-image-align-inline" image-alt="kaizen9_2-1741879635170.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/236817iA016C197685DEFB5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="kaizen9_2-1741879635170.png" alt="kaizen9_2-1741879635170.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;After "Run Test", I got following response, but no expected response again.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="kaizen9_3-1741880275450.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/236824i9171A216A7B30795/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="kaizen9_3-1741880275450.png" alt="kaizen9_3-1741880275450.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;What wrong I am doing?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Can anyone support please? Thanks.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72"&gt;@Dan_Wroblewski&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
